ore after each Aubameyang goal.''<ref name=\"NFT\"/><ref name=\"RSSSF\"/>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1 || 28 March 2009 || [[Stade Mohamed V]], [[Casablanca]], Morocco || {{fb|MAR}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20130 ||align=center| 2\u20131 || [[2010 FIFA World Cup qualification \u2013 CAF Third Round|2010 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 2 || 11 August 2009 || [[Stade de l'Amiti\u00e9]], [[Cotonou]], Benin || {{fb|BEN}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20130 ||align=center| 1\u20131 ||rowspan=\"4\"| [[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 3 || 19 May 2010 || [[Stade Fran\u00e7ois Coty]], [[Ajaccio]], France || {{fb|TOG}} ||align=center| '''2'''\u20130 ||align=center| 3\u20130\n|-\n| 4 || 11 August 2010 || [[Stade du 5 Juillet 1962]], [[Algiers]], Algeria || {{fb|ALG}} ||align=center| '''2'''\u20130 ||align=center| 2\u20131\n|-\n| 5 || 17 November 2010 || [[Parc des Sports Michel Hidalgo|Stade Michel Hidalgo]], [[Sannois]], France || {{fb|SEN}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20132 ||align=center| 1\u20132\n|-\n| 6 || 23 January 2012 ||rowspan=\"2\"| [[Stade d'Angondj\u00e9]], [[Libreville]], Gabon || {{fb|NIG}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20130 ||align=center| 2\u20130 ||rowspan=\"3\"| [[2012 Africa Cup of Nations Group C|2012 Africa Cup of Nations]]\n|-\n| 7 || 27 January 2012 || {{fb|MAR}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20131 ||align=center| 3\u20132\n|-\n| 8 || 31 January 2012 || [[Stade de Franceville]], [[Franceville]], Gabon || {{fb|TUN}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20130 ||align=center| 1\u20130\n|-\n| 9 || 14 October 2012 || Stade d'Angondj\u00e9, Libreville, Gabon || {{fb|TOG}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20132 ||align=center| 1\u20132 || [[2013 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|-\n| 10 ||rowspan=\"3\"| 15 June 2013 ||rowspan=\"3\"| Stade de Franceville, Franceville, Gabon ||rowspan=\"3\"| {{fb|NIG}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20131 ||rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center\"| 4