irmed cases, the first occurrences in the EU.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.sky.com/story/coronavirus-outbreak-hospital-to-be-built-in-five-days-as-death-toll-rises-in-china-11916211|title=Coronavirus outbreak: First confirmed cases in Europe as France declares three infections|last=|first=|date=|website=Sky News|access-date=24 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.lemonde.fr/planete/article/2020/01/24/coronavirus-deux-premiers-cas-confirmes-en-france-a-bordeaux-et-paris_6027158_3244.html|title=Coronavirus : un troisi\u00e8me cas d'infection confirm\u00e9 en France|last=|first=|date=24 January 2020|work=Le Monde.fr|access-date=24 January 2020|language=fr}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.lefigaro.fr/sciences/coronavirus-trois-premiers-cas-confirmes-en-france-20200124|title=Coronavirus: trois premiers cas confirm\u00e9s en France|last1=Jacob|first1=Etienne|date=24 January 2020|work=Le Figaro.fr|language=fr}}</ref> The French Health Minister [[Agn\u00e8s Buzyn]] stated that it is likely other cases would arise in the country.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.trust.org//item/20200124190017-e8ycd/|title=France declares first two confirmed cases of coronavirus|last=|first=|date=24 January 2020|website=Reuters|access-date=}}</ref>\n\nThe first confirmed incidence of human-to-human transmission outside of China was documented by the WHO in Vietnam.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200124-sitrep-4-2019-ncov.pdf?sfvrsn=9272d086_2|title=Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) SITUATION REPORT - 4|last=|first=|date=January 24, 2020|website=World Health Organization|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125232652/https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200124-sitrep-4-2019-ncov.pdf?sfvrsn=9272d086_2|archive-date=January 25, 2020|access-date=}}</ref>\n\nA study by Chinese researchers indicates that people can be symptom-free for several days while the coronavirus is incubating, increasing the risk of contagious infection without forewarning signs.<ref name=\"auto1\" />\n\nA consortium of Chinese medical experts charged by the Chinese CDC with investigating the inception of the virus published their report in ''[[The Lancet]]'', reporting details of 41 first known patients.<ref name=Wang24Jan2020>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20)30185-9/abstract|title=A novel coronavirus outbreak of global health concern|first1=Chen|last1=Wang|first2=Peter W.|last2=Horby|first3=Frederick G.|last3=Hayden|first4=George F.|last4=Gao|date=24 January 2020|journal=The Lancet|volume=0|issue=10223|pages=470\u2013473|via=www.thelancet.com|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(20)30185-9|pmid=31986257|pmc=7135038}}</ref>\n\nBy the end of the day, the entire Hubei province had gone under a city-by-city quarantine, apart from [[Xiangyang]] and [[Shennongjia|Shennongjia Forestry District]].{{citation needed|date=April 2020}} \n\n===25 January===\n[[Communist Party of China|Chinese Communist Party]] [[General Secretary of the Communist Party of China|general secretary]] [[Xi Jinping]] called the \"accelerating spread\" of the coronavirus a \"grave situation\" in a [[Politburo of the Communist Party of China|Party Politburo]] meeting,<ref name=\"People's Daily Online\">{{cite news|url=http://en.people.cn/n3/2020/0125/c90000-9651799.html|title=CPC leadership meets to discuss novel coronavirus prevention, control|date=25 January 2020|work=People's Daily Online|quote=Xi Jinping, general secretary of the CPC Central Committee, chaired the meeting.|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125202946/http://en.people.cn/n3/2020/0125/c90000-9651799.html|archive-date=25 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> and that it was \"mutating\" as Beijing escalates measures to contain the illness.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/coronavirus-news-china-new-year-latest-wuhan-symptoms-virus-uk-france-australia-jinping-a9302011.html|title=Spread of coronavirus 'accelerating', warns China president|date=25 January 2020|website=The Independent|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204232255/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/coronavirus-news-china-new-year-latest-wuhan-symptoms-virus-uk-france-australia-jinping-a9302011.html|archive-date=4 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n'''WHO''' Situation Report 5:<ref>{{Citation|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200125-sitrep-5-2019-ncov.pdf?sfvrsn=429b143d_8|title=Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) Situation Report - 5 25 January 2020|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206035857/https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200125-sitrep-5-2019-ncov.pdf?sfvrsn=429b143d_8|archive-date=6 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAustralia confirmed its first four cases, one in [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://7news.com.au/news/health/first-australian-coronavirus-case-confirmed-in-victoria-c-664530|title=First Australian coronavirus case confirmed in Victoria|last=Daoud|first=Elizabeth|date=January 25, 2020|website=7 News|access-date=}}</ref> and three in [[New South Wales]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2020/jan/25/coronavirus-five-people-in-nsw-being-tested-for-deadly-disease\n|title=Coronavirus: three cases in NSW and one in Victoria as infection reaches Australia|last=Doherty|first=Ben|work=The Guardian|date=25 January 2020|access-date=25 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.smh.com.au/national/victoria/coronavirus-case-confirmed-in-victoria-20200125-p53unk.html\n|title=Coronavirus spreads across Australia amid scramble to find more cases|last2=McCauley|first2=Dana|last1=Cunningham|first1=Melissa|work=Sydney Morning Herald|date=25 January 2020|access-date=25 January 202