han-stayed-at-her-familys-home-in|title=Wuhan virus: Singapore confirms 5th case; patient from Wuhan stayed at her family's home in Ceylon Road|last1=Toh|first1=Yong Chuan|date=28 January 2020|work=The Straits Times|accessdate=28 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128003837/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/wuhan-virus-singapore-confirms-5th-case-patient-from-wuhan-stayed-at-her-familys-home-in|archive-date=28 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Germany confirmed its first case in [[Bavaria]], a case of domestic transmission.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spiegel.de/wissenschaft/medizin/corona-virus-erster-fall-in-deutschland-bestaetigt-a-19843b8d-8694-451f-baf7-0189d3356f99|title=Erster Fall des Coronavirus in Deutschland best\u00e4tigt|date=2020-01-28|language=de|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/en/germany-confirms-first-case-of-coronavirus/a-52169007|title=Germany confirms first case of coronavirus {{!}} DW {{!}} 27.01.2020|website=DW.COM|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128022332/https://www.dw.com/en/germany-confirms-first-case-of-coronavirus/a-52169007|archive-date=2020-01-28|url-status=live}}</ref> Taiwan reports its first case of domestic transmission of the coronavirus.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/wuhan-virus-taiwan-reports-first-case-of-domestic-coronavirus-transmission|title=Wuhan virus: Taiwan reports first case of domestic coronavirus transmission|date=28 January 2020|website=The Straits Times|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207192737/https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/wuhan-virus-taiwan-reports-first-case-of-domestic-coronavirus-transmission|archive-date=7 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n[[Beijing]] reports its first death from coronavirus.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200127-beijing-reports-capital-s-first-death-from-coronavi