f>{{cite news|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/wuhan-virus-singapore-new-confirmed-cases-coronavirus-12364556|title=Singapore confirms 3 new cases of Wuhan virus; total of 10 infected|accessdate=2020-01-29|website=CNA|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129112711/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/wuhan-virus-singapore-new-confirmed-cases-coronavirus-12364556|archive-date=2020-01-29|url-status=live}}</ref> Malaysia confirms three additional cases, bringing its total to seven.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/01/560544/three-more-positive-coronavirus-cases-malaysia-bringing-total-7|title=Three more positive coronavirus cases in Malaysia, bringing total to 7|publisher=New Straits Times|date=2020-01-29|url-status=live|accessdate=2020-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129012136/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/01/560544/three-more-positive-coronavirus-cases-malaysia-bringing-total-7|archive-date=2020-01-29}}</ref> Japan reports four additional cases, including a tour bus guide that was on the same bus as one of the cases confirmed on 28 January<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200129/k10012264621000.html|title=\u30d0\u30b9\u3067\u30ac\u30a4\u30c9 \u5927\u962a\u306e\u5973\u6027 \u30a6\u30a4\u30eb\u30b9\u306b\u611f\u67d3 \u5948\u826f\u306e\u904b\u8ee2\u624b\u3068\u540c\u4e57|last=\u65e5\u672c\u653e\u9001\u5354\u4f1a|language=Japanese|location=Japan|website=[[NHK]]|accessdate=2020-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129123513/https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200129/k10012264621000.html|archive-date=29 January 2020|url-status=dead}}</ref> and three evacuated from Wuhan.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200130/k10012264981000.html|title=\u65b0\u578b\u80ba\u708e 29\u65e5\u5e30\u56fd\u306e\uff13\u4eba\u611f\u67d3\u78ba\u8a8d \u3046\u30612\u4eba\u306f\u767a\u71b1\u306a\u3069\u75c7\u72b6\u306a\u3057|website=[[NHK]]|access-date=2020-