health-news/coronavirus-spreads-first-time-u-s-cdc-says-n1126566|title=Coronavirus spreads for first time in U.S., CDC says|website=www.nbcnews.com|access-date=2020-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130174627/https://www.nbcnews.com/health/health-news/coronavirus-spreads-first-time-u-s-cdc-says-n1126566|archive-date=2020-01-30|url-status=live}}</ref> This is the first confirmed case of human to human transmission within the United States.  Mr. Azar, Dr. Redfield and Dr. Anthony S. Fauci agreed that a ban on travel from the epidemic\u2019s center could buy some time to put into place prevention and testing measures.  Dr. Redfield said in an interview that \u201cThere was so much we didn\u2019t know about this virus,\u201d\u201cWe were rapidly understanding it was much more transmissible, that it had a great ability to go global.\u201d <ref name=\":1\" />\n\n===31 January===\n'''WHO''' Situation Report 11:<ref>{{Citation|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200131-sitrep-11-ncov.pdf?sfvrsn=de7c0f7_4|title=Novel Coronavirus(2019-nCoV) Situation Report - 11}}</ref>\n\nThe [[United Kingdom]] and [[Russia]] confirmed their first coronavirus infections.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2020/01/31/coronavirus-symptoms-britain-russia-who-wuhan-emergency/4620574002/|title=Britain, Russia report first cases of coronavirus as illness spreads to 20 countries|first=Doug|last=Stanglin|website=USA TODAY|access-date=2020-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206103724/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2020/01/31/coronavirus-symptoms-britain-russia-who-wuhan-emergency/4620574002/|archive-date=2020-02-06|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-51325192|title=Coronavirus: Two cases confirmed in UK|accessdate=31 January 2020|website=BBC|date=31 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131100345/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-5